headline: ResMed Announces Participation in the 43rd Annual J.P. Morgan Healthcare Conference
summary: SAN DIEGO, Jan. 06, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- ResMed (NYSE: RMD, ASX: RMD) today announced Mick Farrell, chairman and chief executive officer, and Dr. Carlos Nunez, chief medical officer, will present at the 43rd Annual J.P. Morgan Healthcare Conference on Monday, January 13, 2025, beginning at approximately 3:00 p.m. (Pacific Standard Time) in San Francisco, CA. More information about this event, including access to the live, audio-only webcast, may be accessed by visiting https://investor.resme
